      "content": "it's not even \"difficult\" though. difficult implies there's something to fix. but how do you fix something that isn't there? it's just empty. i feel like i've been playing a character for years to make everyone else happy, and now the character is all that's left. the actual \"me\" is just... gone. there's nothing to come back to.",
